## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="a3fdd-102">在<xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher>，当被通知文件发生更改，这些更改组件的缓冲区中创建并传递给应用程序编程接口 (Api) 的系统存储。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a3fdd-102">In a <xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher>, when you are notified of file changes, the system stores those changes in a buffer the component creates and passes to the Application Programming Interfaces (APIs).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a3fdd-103">如果短时间内有很多更改，则缓冲区可能轻松溢出，从而导致异常抛出，这实质上会丢失所有更改。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a3fdd-103">If there are many changes in a short time, the buffer can easily overflow, resulting in an exception being thrown, which essentially loses all changes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a3fdd-104">若要防止缓冲区溢出，请使用<xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher.NotifyFilter%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>和<xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher.IncludeSubdirectories%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>属性，以筛选掉不需要的更改通知。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a3fdd-104">To keep the buffer from overflowing, use the <xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher.NotifyFilter%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> and <xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher.IncludeSubdirectories%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> properties to filter out your unwanted change notifications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a3fdd-105">也可以通过 <xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher.InternalBufferSize%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> 属性增加内部缓冲区的大小。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a3fdd-105">You can also increase the size of the internal buffer through the <xref:System.IO.FileSystemWatcher.InternalBufferSize%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="a3fdd-106">但是，增加缓冲区的大小非常昂贵，因此保持缓冲区尽可能小。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="a3fdd-106">However, increasing the size of the buffer is expensive, so keep the buffer as small as possible.</span></span>  
  
   
  
